#
# # Application Config
# # VITE_APP_NAME="Weather App"
# # VITE_APP_VERSION=1.0.0
#
# REMEMBER:
# - All VITE_ variables are PUBLIC (embedded in bundle)
# - Update .env.example when adding new variables
# - Document purpose and how to obtain values
# - Update GitHub secrets for CI/CD

